data.text:
Image: AP Images

Zsa Zsa and Eva Gabor have been acting icons since their first appearances on the silver screen. Whether they appeared in popular television shows, as the stars of movies, or as the guests on late-night talk shows, the Gabor sisters made it clear that they were separate, yet equally powerful, entertainment forces to be reckoned with.

This didn't stifle their good-naturedness nor their social popularity. The Gabor sisters were well-known for being social butterflies, making plenty of elite Hollywood friends throughout their careers. They maintained a sense of humor around their celebrity status; if there was ever a piece of gossip about her, Eva had a habit of teasing that it was actually her sister, Zsa Zsa, the paparazzi should be questioning.

Though you may love them equally, we want to know if you can tell which sister we're talking about. How well do you know these two Gabor sisters?
